# Plain HTML in JSX

This project does **not** use Framer Motion. There is no `framer-motion` dependency.

## Layout markup

- Use standard HTML elements only: `div`, `section`, `article`, `header`, `nav`, `main`, `aside`, `footer`, `button`, `ul`, `li`, etc.
- Do **not** use `motion.div`, `motion.section`, `import { motion } from 'framer-motion'`, or a bare `<motion>` tag as a layout wrapper.
- When scaffolding structure, default to `div` / `section` — never reach for Motion components out of habit.

```tsx
// ❌ BAD — not in this repo
<motion className={styles.inner}>
<motion.div className={styles.layout}>

// ✅ GOOD
<div className={styles.inner}>
<div className={styles.layout}>
```
